ENTRY       EC 3.2.1.58                 Enzyme
NAME        glucan 1,3-beta-glucosidase;
            exo-1,3-beta-glucosidase;
            beta-1,3-glucan exo-hydrolase;
            exo (1->3)-glucanohydrolase;
            1,3-beta-glucan glucohydrolase
CLASS       Hydrolases;
            Glycosylases;
